From david at hartbit.com  Fri Dec  4 02:14:04 2015
From: david at hartbit.com (David Hart)
Date: Fri, 4 Dec 2015 09:14:04 +0100
Subject: [swift-evolution] [swift-corelibs-dev] Proposal: Swift Open
