> On Thu, Dec 3, 2015, at 09:47 PM, ChanMaxthon wrote:
>> How about this C code when rewritten in Swift:
>>
>> char *blk_xor(char *dst, const char *src, size_t len)
>> {
>>  const char *sp = src;
>>  for (char *dp = dst; sp - src < len; sp++, dp++)
>>    *dp ^= *sp;
>>  return dst;
>> }
>>
>> Sent from my iPhone
>>
